<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Under Construction</title>
  <style>
    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
                   "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f0f;
      color: #eaeaea;
    }

    .container {
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .box {
        max-width: 520px;
    }

    .lang-menu {
        position: fixed;
        top: 20px;
        right: 20px;
        color: #757575;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        padding: 8px 16px;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: bold;
        z-index: 1000;
    }
    .lang-menu a {
        margin: 0 5px;
        color: #2e1d12;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1em;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .lang-menu a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    html[lang="en"] [lang]:not([lang="en"]),
    html[lang="es"] [lang]:not([lang="es"]),
    html[lang="fr"] [lang]:not([lang="fr"]) {
        display: none;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #b5b5b5;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .divider {
      width: 60px;
      height: 2px;
      background: #444;
      margin: 1.5rem auto;
    }

    footer {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #666;
    }

    .container a {
        color: #7ab8ff;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
        text-underline-offset: 3px;
        transition: color 0.15s ease, text-decoration-color 0.15s ease;
    }

    .container a:visited {
        color: #9aa7ff;
    }

    .container a:hover,
    .container a:focus-visible {
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .container a:active {
        color: #cfe3ff;
    }
  </style>
  <script src="./language.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  #include "body_header.html"

  <div class="container">
    <div class="box">
      <h1>
        <span lang="en">Under Construction</span>
        <span lang="es">En construcción</span>
        <span lang="fr">En cours de construction</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div lang="en">
        <p>This site is currently being built.<br />
          Please check back soon.</p>
        <p>Looking for the form&#63;<br />
          It&#39;s <a href="./rsvp.html">here</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div lang="es">
        <p>Este sitio web está actualmente en construcción.<br />
          Vuelve pronto.</p>
        <p>¿Buscas el formulario&#63;<br />
          Est&#225; <a href="./rsvp.html">aqu&#237;</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div lang="fr">
        <p>Ce site est actuellement en cours de construction.<br />
          Revenez bient&#244;t.</p>
        <p>Vous cherchez le formulaire&#63;<br />
          Il est <a href="./rsvp.html">ici</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
